back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hmp1665703544187.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hmp1665703544187.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hmp1665703544187.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hmp1665703544187\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      XML Attribute\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__xml_attribute_531531\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An XML attribute is an identifier associated with an XML tag. It has a unique name in the context of the tag, and a string value. A tag can have any number of attributes, including none.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__topic_d178061e1_d178062e1_d178063e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178064e1_d178065e1_d178066e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">tagName</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">attribName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=\"</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"&gt;</code>…<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">tagName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178067e1_d178068e1_d178069e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">tagName</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">attribName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=\"</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"/&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__topic_d142537e1_d142538e1_d142539e1_d142540e1_d142541e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d849068e109\">\n                       \n Conversion to Struct\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178073e1_d178074e1_d178075e1\">An XML element converts to a Struct with the name <var class=\"keyword varname\">attribName</var>, and annotation tag <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlClass = attribute</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__topic_d142542e1_d142543e1_d142544e1_d142545e1_d142546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d849068e124\">\n                       \n Annotations\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178079e1_d178080e1_d178081e1\">The Struct for an XML element can have the following annotations:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54578e1_d54579e1_d54580e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlClass = attribute</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54581e1_d54582e1_d54583e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlNamespaceURI =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54584e1_d54585e1_d54586e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlNamespaceAlias =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">prefix</var>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178082e1_d178083e1_d178084e1\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlToStruct</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/schema</code> is used, and if the data type is defined in a schema with a namespace, it can have addition annotations:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54587e1_d54588e1_d54589e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlDataType =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DataType</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54590e1_d54591e1_d54592e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlTypeCategory = simple</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">complex</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__li_d54593e1_d54594e1_d54595e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlTypeNamespace =</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__p_d178085e1_d178086e1_d178087e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdu1665702698788.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdu1665702698788.html\" title=\"When converting between XML and Structs using xmlToStruct or structToXml, you can set and retrieve annotations that provide information that guides the conversion (or reverse conversion).\">Struct Annotations for XML</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__section_eyq_bg3_ddc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d849068e213\">Example: XML to Struct Conversion: Attributes </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">XML element with attribute and value:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__pre_gry_bg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;para audience=\"admin\"&gt;text&lt;/para&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">String returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dbgString</span> after conversion:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__pre_iry_bg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[]\n [para]\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = element\n [aurience] = admin\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = attribute\n [] = text</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">/schema</code> is used and the schema specifies a data\n               type for priority:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__pre_jry_bg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[]\n [p]\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = element\n [priority] = 2\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = attribute\n [xmlDataType] = decimal\n [xmlTypeNamespace] = http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema\n [] = text</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">You can get the values of Structs using Struct access operators. For\n               example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hmp1665703544187__pre_kry_bg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vValue = vStruct-&gt;p ; Result: vValue = \"text\"\nvClass = vStruct-&gt;p-&gt;$tags-&gt;xmlClass ; Result: vClass = \"element\"\nvValue = vStruct-&gt;p-&gt;priority ; Result: vValue = \"2\"\nvClass = vStruct-&gt;p-&gt;priority-&gt;$tags-&gt;xmlClass ; Result: vClass = \"attribute\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528285\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528285\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "XML Attribute Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 XML Attribute An XML attribute is an identifier associated with an XML tag. It has a unique name in the context of the tag, and a string value. A tag can have any number of attributes, including none. < tagName attribName =\" Value \"> … </ tagName > < tagName attribName =\" Value \"/> Conversion to Struct An XML element converts to a Struct with the name attribName , and annotation tag xmlClass = attribute . Annotations The Struct for an XML element can have the following annotations: xmlClass = attribute xmlNamespaceURI = URI xmlNamespaceAlias = prefix If xmlToStruct /schema is used, and if the data type is defined in a schema with a namespace, it can have addition annotations: xmlDataType = DataType xmlTypeCategory = simple | complex xmlTypeNamespace = For more information, see Struct Annotations for XML . Example: XML to Struct Conversion: Attributes XML element with attribute and value: <para audience=\"admin\">text</para> Copy String returned by $dbgString after conversion: [] [para] [$tags] [xmlClass] = element [aurience] = admin [$tags] [xmlClass] = attribute [] = text Copy If /schema is used and the schema specifies a data type for priority: [] [p] [$tags] [xmlClass] = element [priority] = 2 [$tags] [xmlClass] = attribute [xmlDataType] = decimal [xmlTypeNamespace] = http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema [] = text Copy You can get the values of Structs using Struct access operators. For example: vValue = vStruct->p ; Result: vValue = \"text\" vClass = vStruct->p->$tags->xmlClass ; Result: vClass = \"element\" vValue = vStruct->p->priority ; Result: vValue = \"2\" vClass = vStruct->p->priority->$tags->xmlClass ; Result: vClass = \"attribute\" Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}